# No Emojis

Do not use emojis anywhere:

- Source code
- Docstrings
- Comments
- Markdown files
- Documentation
- Logging messages
- Error messages
- Commit messages
- Test output

Use plain text indicators instead:

| Instead of | Use |
|------------|-----|
| Checkmark emoji | `[x]` or `PASS` |
| X emoji | `[ ]` or `FAIL` |
| Warning emoji | `WARNING:` |
| Fire emoji | (nothing, just describe the issue) |
